<p>Saturday 17 March</p>
<p>The bombardment continued all night.  Bapaume fell at 4 a.m.  The 30th Batt. were the first Australian troops to enter the town.  The 8th Brigade &amp; the 29th Tommy Division took it.  Le Transloy has also fallen.  Concert in our camp tonight.<br/>List of 30 names read out including mine.  These have to leave for the line at 6 a.m. tomorrow.<br/>Bapaume is in flames so also are the surrounding villages.</p>
